com.mariangolea.fintracker.banks.csvparser.api.transaction

Class TransactionCategorizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mariangolea.fintracker.banks.csvparser.api.transaction.TransactionCategorizer

  • public class TransactionCategorizer
extends Object
    Produces a structured model from given list of parsed bank transactions and a user preferences object.
    Accesses:
    • user selected time slot (whether splitting should be made based on months or years) which can be used as rows in the table view of transactions.
    • top most categories (can be used as columns in the table view of transactions).
    • list of parsed bank transactions.

    Produces a map where keys are time slots and values are a list of tree like objects representing top most category currency operations.
